        "@id": "https://hologram.os/conformance/os2#own-mcp",
        "dcterms:title": "Ownership is usable by AI agents over MCP (ADR-053, layer 3) — own_verify · own_settle · own_passport are advertised, JSON-Schema'd tools on the canonical Hologram MCP server returning SELF-VERIFYING results (Law L5): an agent verifies who owns an object, settles value against proven title (a tampered title releases nothing), and reads an ownership passport without trusting any server; an agent acquires ownership by signing a Title with its own self-sovereign key — agents are owners + counterparties on the one substrate"
      },
